description: Creates a new cognitive skillset in an Azure Search service or updates the skillset if it already exists.

skillset_name.description: The name of the skillset to create or update.

prefer.description: For HTTP PUT requests, instructs the service to return the created/updated resource on success.

cognitiveservices.description: Details about cognitive services to be used when running skills.

skillset.description: The skillset containing one or more cognitive skills to create or update in an Azure Search service.

client_request_id.description: The tracking ID sent with the request to help with debugging.

skills.description: A list of skills in the skillset.
